      <body>
         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">14/6/94. ¶  ¶ Tired out I am writing these lines in the midnight hours, dear Mr Tepper, but if a letter is just laid aside, it may remain completely unanswered. Nevertheless in 1893 I wrote about 6000...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="de">94.06.14</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="de">To Otto Tepper</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="de">RB MSS M198, Library, Royal Botanic Gardens Melbourne.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="de">14/6/94.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg style="">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ermüdet schreibe ich diese Zeilen in der Mitternachts Stunde, lieber Herr Tepper, aber wenn ein Brief erst aus der Hand gelegt wird, möchte er ganz unbeantwortet bleibe. Trotzdessen, dass eich in 1893 etwa 6000 Breife schrieb oder deren Equivalent.</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg style="">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Die Pflanze, welche Sie mir senden jetzt ist eine <name key="Pomaderris">Pomaderris</name>, aber es wird am Besten sein, mit der Bestimmung der Art zu warten, bis auch </seg>
               <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">reife Früchte</hi>
               </seg>
               <seg style=""> herbeigeschafft werden können.</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">Sie ehrend, der Ihre</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg style="">Ziemlich viel Manuscr. für den Suppl. Band ist fertig, aber da fast täglich neue Sammlungen hier eintreffen, welche neue Standorte geben, habe ich es wünschenswerth gehalten, den </seg>
               <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">Druck</hi>
               </seg>
               <seg style=""> nicht zu beschleunigen. Die Arbeit eines solchen Bandes ist viel schwerer als die irgend eines der ersten 7 Bände.</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg style="">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Recht gern werde ich auch die Pflanzen, von denen Sie sprechen, benennen u Ihnen die Ex zurücksenden. Es würde mir </seg>
               <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">schaden,</hi>
               </seg>
               <seg style=""> verliesse in dieser Zeit der </seg>
               <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">Finanznoth</hi>
               </seg>
               <seg style=""> auch nur für </seg>
               <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">kurze</hi>
               </seg>
               <seg style=""> </seg>
               <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">Zeit</hi>
               </seg>
               <seg style=""> </seg>
               <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">meinen</hi>
               </seg>
               <seg style=""> </seg>
               <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">Posten</hi>
               </seg>
               <seg style="">! </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg style="">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Herr Holtze wird dies auch einsehen. Ist Dr Brown von Victoria dort zurückgekehrt.</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">Ihr Sie Ehrenden</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">14/6/94.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Tired out I am writing these lines in the midnight hours, dear Mr Tepper, but if a letter is just laid aside, it may remain completely unanswered. Nevertheless in 1893 I wrote about 6000 letters or their equivalents.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>The plant that you send me now is a <seg style="font-style: italic; ">
                  <name key="Pomaderris">Pomaderris</name>
               </seg>, but it will be best to wait with the determination of the species until <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">ripe fruits</hi>
               </seg> can also be collected.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Respectfully your</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Rather a lot of manuscript for the supplementary volume<note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>The proposed but never published supplement to the <seg style="font-style: italic; ">Flora australiensis</seg>. See O. Tepper to M, 12 June 1894, where Tepper inquired about the supplement's progress.</p>
               </note> is ready, but since new collections arrive here almost daily that give new localities, I have thought it desirable not to speed up the <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">printing</hi>
               </seg>. The work of such a volume is much harder than that of any of the first 7 volumes.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I will very willingly also name the plants of which you speak and send you back the specimens. It would <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">injure</hi>
               </seg> me, if I left <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">my</hi>
               </seg>
               <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">post</hi>
               </seg> in these times of <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">financial problems</hi>
               </seg> even only for a <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">short</hi>
               </seg>
               <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">time</hi>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Mr Holtze will also see this. Has Dr Brown<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>i.e. John Harris Browne; see M to O. Tepper, 27 January 1894 (in this edition as 94-01-27a). No evidence of <seg style="">Browne's visiting Melbourne</seg> has been found, nor has any evidence been found that his brother William James Browne had been in Australia in 1894 prior to his death in Eastbourne, England on 4 December.</p>
               </note> returned there from Victoria.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Your respectful</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">
               <name key="Pomaderris">Pomaderris</name>
            </p>
         </div>
      </body>
